  "texts": [
    "For a fair comparison with prior works mentioned above, we report standard micro Precision (Prec.), Recall (Rec.",
    "), and F1-score (F1.)",
    "as our three evaluation metrics.",
    "Meanwhile, we implement distinct matching rules for each version of the datasets.",
    "In the case of NYT and WebNLG datasets, an extracted relational triple is regarded correct only if all words of both entities and the relation type precisely align with the ground truth."
  ],
